# Tech Stack

**Use latest stable versions** for all dependencies. Do not copy pinned versions from older projects; install or upgrade to current stable so new projects stay up to date.

## Core

| Technology       | Notes                                                            |
| ---------------- | ---------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **React**        | React with react-dom; use latest stable.                         |
| **TypeScript**   | Strict mode, ES2022 target. Use latest stable.                   |
| **Vite**         | Build tool and dev server. Use latest stable.                    |
| **Tailwind CSS** | Use Tailwind v4 via `@tailwindcss/vite`; use Tailwind v4 syntax. |

## UI & Styling

| Library                            | Usage                                                                                                               |
| ---------------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **@abumble/design-system**         | Primary UI components (Popover, NotFound, UnderConstruction, utils, types). Use latest compatible version.          |
| **Shadcn (new-york)**              | Style: `new-york`, baseColor: `zinc`, cssVariables: true. Add components with `pnpx shadcn@latest add <component>`. |
| **Radix**                          | Via design-system/shadcn; not installed directly.                                                                   |
| **class-variance-authority (cva)** | For component variants.                                                                                             |
| **clsx**                           | Class name composition.                                                                                             |
| **tailwind-merge**                 | Merge Tailwind classes (use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` or design-system).                                            |
| **lucide-react**                   | Icons (components.json: iconLibrary: "lucide").                                                                     |
| **tw-animate-css**                 | Animations.                                                                                                         |

## Data & Routing

| Library                     | Notes                            |
| --------------------------- | -------------------------------- |
| **@tanstack/react-query**   | Use latest stable.               |
| **@tanstack/react-router**  | Use latest stable.               |
| **@tanstack/router-plugin** | Vite plugin; match router major. |

## Tooling

- **ESLint**: @tanstack/eslint-config (latest).
- **Prettier**: Latest stable. Prefer: semi: false, singleQuote: true, trailingComma: "all", useTabs: true.
- **Vitest** + **@testing-library/react** for tests (latest stable).

## Adding UI Components

- Prefer **@abumble/design-system** when a component exists there.
- For net-new shadcn-style components, use: `pnpx shadcn@latest add <component>` so the correct Tailwind v4 + aliases are used.
